{"title":"Contact","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Contact","body-classes":"page-title","page-layout":"full"},"headingText":"Dr. Jason S. Tsukahara, Ph.D.","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n::: {.page-header}\n\n::: {.header-text}\n\n::: {.header-title}\nCONTACT\n:::\n\n::: {.header-subtitle}\nGet in touch with the CALM Lab.\n:::\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n::: {.section-shell}\n\n::: {.grid-2}\n\n::: {.card .card-lg .is-blue}\n\n::: {.card-body .card-body-lg}\n\n<div class=\"icon-badge icon-badge-blue\">\n  <i class=\"bi bi-envelope\"></i>\n</div>\n\n\n::: {style=\"color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: -.5rem;\"}\nPrincipal Investigator\n:::\n\n**Email**: jason.tsukahara@miami.edu <a onclick=\"copyEmail(this); return false;\" data-copy=\"jason.tsukahara@miami.edu\" title=\"Copy email\" class=\"copy-email-link\"><i class=\"bi bi-copy\"></i></a>\n\n::: {style=\"line-height: 1;\"}\n**Office**: building, room number\n\n**Office Phone**: office phone here\n\n**Mailing Address**: address here\n:::\n\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n::: {.card .card-lg .is-blue}\n\n::: {.card-body .card-body-lg}\n\n<div class=\"icon-badge icon-badge-green\">\n  <i class=\"bi bi-people\"></i>\n</div>\n\n### Contact the Lab\n\n::: {style=\"color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: -.5rem;\"}\nGeneral Inquiries\n:::\n\n**Email**: jason.tsukahara@miami.edu <a onclick=\"copyEmail(this); return false;\" data-copy=\"jason.tsukahara@miami.edu\" title=\"Copy email\" class=\"copy-email-link\"><i class=\"bi bi-copy\"></i></a>\n\n::: {style=\"line-height: 1;\"}\n**Lab Location:** building, room number\n\n**Lab Phone**: office phone here\n\n**Mailing Address**: address here\n:::\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n::: {.section-shell}\n\n::: {.grid-2}\n\n::: {.card .card-lg .is-green}\n\n::: {.card-body .card-body-lg}\n\n<div class=\"icon-badge icon-badge-blue\">\n  <i class=\"bi bi-envelope\"></i>\n</div>\n\n### Join the Lab\n\n::: {style=\"color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: -.5rem;\"}\nInterested in joining the CALM Lab?\n:::\n\n::: {style=\"margin-bottom: 2rem;\"}\nWe are currently recruiting for:\n\n- Undergraduate Research Assistant\n:::\n\n**Email**: jason.tsukahara@miami.edu <a onclick=\"copyEmail(this); return false;\" data-copy=\"jason.tsukahara@miami.edu\" title=\"Copy email\" class=\"copy-email-link\"><i class=\"bi bi-copy\"></i></a>\n\nCheck out our [Projects](projects/index.qmd) to learn more about our research, and feel free to reach out with any questions or to express interest in joining the lab!\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n\n\n:::\n\n:::\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n::: {.page-header}\n\n::: {.header-text}\n\n::: {.header-title}\nCONTACT\n:::\n\n::: {.header-subtitle}\nGet in touch with the CALM Lab.\n:::\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n::: {.section-shell}\n\n::: {.grid-2}\n\n::: {.card .card-lg .is-blue}\n\n::: {.card-body .card-body-lg}\n\n<div class=\"icon-badge icon-badge-blue\">\n  <i class=\"bi bi-envelope\"></i>\n</div>\n\n### Dr. Jason S. Tsukahara, Ph.D.\n\n::: {style=\"color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: -.5rem;\"}\nPrincipal Investigator\n:::\n\n**Email**: jason.tsukahara@miami.edu <a onclick=\"copyEmail(this); return false;\" data-copy=\"jason.tsukahara@miami.edu\" title=\"Copy email\" class=\"copy-email-link\"><i class=\"bi bi-copy\"></i></a>\n\n::: {style=\"line-height: 1;\"}\n**Office**: building, room number\n\n**Office Phone**: office phone here\n\n**Mailing Address**: address here\n:::\n\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n::: {.card .card-lg .is-blue}\n\n::: {.card-body .card-body-lg}\n\n<div class=\"icon-badge icon-badge-green\">\n  <i class=\"bi bi-people\"></i>\n</div>\n\n### Contact the Lab\n\n::: {style=\"color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: -.5rem;\"}\nGeneral Inquiries\n:::\n\n**Email**: jason.tsukahara@miami.edu <a onclick=\"copyEmail(this); return false;\" data-copy=\"jason.tsukahara@miami.edu\" title=\"Copy email\" class=\"copy-email-link\"><i class=\"bi bi-copy\"></i></a>\n\n::: {style=\"line-height: 1;\"}\n**Lab Location:** building, room number\n\n**Lab Phone**: office phone here\n\n**Mailing Address**: address here\n:::\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n::: {.section-shell}\n\n::: {.grid-2}\n\n::: {.card .card-lg .is-green}\n\n::: {.card-body .card-body-lg}\n\n<div class=\"icon-badge icon-badge-blue\">\n  <i class=\"bi bi-envelope\"></i>\n</div>\n\n### Join the Lab\n\n::: {style=\"color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: -.5rem;\"}\nInterested in joining the CALM Lab?\n:::\n\n::: {style=\"margin-bottom: 2rem;\"}\nWe are currently recruiting for:\n\n- Undergraduate Research Assistant\n:::\n\n**Email**: jason.tsukahara@miami.edu <a onclick=\"copyEmail(this); return false;\" data-copy=\"jason.tsukahara@miami.edu\" title=\"Copy email\" class=\"copy-email-link\"><i class=\"bi bi-copy\"></i></a>\n\nCheck out our [Projects](projects/index.qmd) to learn more about our research, and feel free to reach out with any questions or to express interest in joining the lab!\n\n:::\n\n:::\n\n\n\n:::\n\n:::\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl